      <ol id="ol_n3n_lkz_qzb" class="- topic/ol ">
         <li class="- topic/li ">This document describes how to configure a Machine Server to back up critical files.
            Ideally, one backup machine server will be operational on the network for every furnace
            that has machines requiring a machine server. This procedure assumes that SWSet 223
            (SCS-0237-GR223) or higher is being used.</li>
         <li class="- topic/li ">This document supersedes instructions provided in the IDS Electronic Service &amp;
            Reference Manual, Appendix A.</li>
      </ol>
